<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="experiment-vi">experiment <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪk'sperɪmənt/    美 /ɪk'sperɪmənt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>做实验 / 试验；尝试：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>experiment on</strong> animals 
用动物做实验</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Scientists are still <strong>experimenting with</strong> cloning mammals. 
科学家还在试验克隆哺乳动物。</p><footer>人教⑧ – 2</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The school is <strong>experimenting with</strong> new teaching methods.
这所学校正在尝试新的教学法。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>experimental /ɪkˌsperɪ'mentl/ adj   </p></div>